reviewText: Lame. Not much actual interview of anyone. Continuous annoying music.
If your a Hunger Games Fan, buy this! It may be boring for a younger audience, but its very thought provoking. Love this! I added it to my collection!
Beyond the "young adult" labeling, this is a serious film. Popcorn for the young, but thought-provoking insights and themes for adults. Young cast is helped by top-notch  supporting cast.
